### GET request to example server
GET http://localhost:8080/site/api/favourites/

### get-favourites - Simple Request
POST http://localhost:8080/site/api/favourites/get-favourites
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "uuids": [
    "8b4a3c11-8b84-4aa0-bccf-f407d18c1c44"
  ]
}

### get-favourites - Multiple Documents
POST http://localhost:8080/site/api/favourites/get-favourites
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "uuids": [
    "8b4a3c11-8b84-4aa0-bccf-f407d18c1c44",
    "4d302e29-93dd-4157-9df9-bbd741bb12a0",
    "ab8d2643-1517-4a6a-aa86-f5a9c8b5e2c3",
    "bc5bec32-9cbc-45a7-855b-342008ad8ef9",
    "a2ca775b-0df5-4e2c-900c-c51c9f2e5d47"
  ]
}

### get-favourites - Spanish Language
POST http://localhost:8080/site/api/favourites/get-favourites
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "uuids": [
    "ae3f6897-ae12-4e53-8b59-f211b46eca3a",
