### get-favourites - Non-existing content
POST http://localhost:8080/site/api/favourites/get-favourites
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "uuids": [
    "deadbeef-abba-baba-daba-decadefacade",
    "facefeed-abba-baba-daba-decadefacade",
    "cafebabe-abba-baba-daba-decadefacade"
  ]
}